        "### Reinforcement Learning Setup\n",
        "\n",
        "In this part, I implement a simple Q-Learning model where the agent can take three actions:\n",
        "- Hold\n",
        "- Buy\n",
        "- Sell\n",
        "\n",
        "The reward is based on profit or loss."
      ],
